#some facts on penalties

#age group of players who played in the season
under20 = pldf[pldf['Age']<=20]
age20_25= pldf[(pldf['Age']>20) & (pldf['Age']<=25)]
age25_30= pldf[(pldf['Age']>25) & (pldf['Age']<=30)]
Above30 = pldf[pldf['Age']>30]
x = np.array([under20['Name'].count(),age20_25['Name'].count(),age25_30['Name'].count(),Above30['Name'].count()])
labelsage=['<=20','20-25','25-30','>30']
plt.title('Players in different age groups', fontsize=20)
plt.pie(x,labels=labelsage,autopct="%.1f%%")
plt.show()
